  "title": "chore(example): stop promoting the dev example as the gh-pages",
  "body": "Everything we show on gh-pages should be easy to read as code, so no build.\n\nSince we still want to keep an easily runnable dev environment and want to present nice things to our users viewing the source, we should stop publishing the example dev app on gh pages.\n\nWhat we will present is the instantsearch-demo using instantsearch.js which do not have any build process but just regular js files.\n\nTODO:\n- [x] remove the gh pages link in the github project description\n- [ ] modify the release process to stop pushing the example dev app to gh-pages \n\nFixes #197 \n",
